  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2889334">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2889334/" class="title-link">探寻中国古迹，开创历史的新纪元</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2889334"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/29144146/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/29144146/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">诵读清香</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-12-25"
      class="main-meta">2009-12-25 20:55:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2889334_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  中国有着博大精深的文化底蕴，有着许多不可解得的神秘面纱，但随着考古工作者的细心探寻，让中国的古老的面貌开始在国人面前逐渐呈现，这不能不让每一个中国人为之骄傲。通过考古的进一步发现，人们会对探寻中国的古老文化有着更为浓厚的兴趣，会使更多的人投入到探寻中国古迹...

